                    "name": "Worry Prey",
                    "type": "stat_block_section",
                    "text": "<b>Requirements</b> The cu sith has a Large or smaller creature grabbed in its jaws; <b>Effect</b> The cu sith viciously shakes its prey. The cu sith makes a jaws Strike against the grabbed creature with a +2 circumstance bonus to the attack roll. If the cu sith hits, it deals jaws damage, maintains its Grab, and attempts an <a aonid=\"3\" game-obj=\"Skills\">Athletics</a> check to <a aonid=\"41\" game-obj=\"Actions\">Disarm</a> its target of anything it is holding. On a miss, the cu sith releases the creature.",
